VALUES
('bookkeeper-moex-00962', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '抒情天團八月雪將於X8年間舉辦四場演唱會，預計於每季底在小巨蛋開唱。門票於X7年10月開 賣至12月底截止，所有門票全數售出，共得款80,000千元。該樂團採曆年制，請問X8年4月1日 之預收門票收入餘額為： 千元  千元  千元  千元', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00963', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '美顏堂生產且銷售化妝保養品，X6 年底於倉庫盤點存貨時，計有庫存商品$1,500,000；另美顏堂在 全國藥妝店之寄銷品有$2,500,000。經查，X6 年底尚有銷往北美及歐洲之在途商品各一批，金額分 別為$1,200,000（太平洋線，起運點交貨）及$1,600,000（大西洋線，目的地交貨）。請問美顏堂X6 年底期末存貨應為：', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00964', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '近期由於電子被動元件價格上漲，國鉅公司懷疑存貨有失竊情事，於是調閱X6年度相關資料如下： 期初存貨  進    貨  進貨退回 成  本  $35,000  $255,000  $15,000 零售價  50,000  472,000  22,000 X6年度銷貨收入$400,000，銷貨退回$20,000，而期末實地盤點存貨之成本為$30,000。請問估計存貨 失竊之成本為：', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00965', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '豐星鋼鐵廠X5年的相關成本資料如下： 直接原料存貨（1/1）  $165,000  直接原料進貨  $3,816,000 直接原料存貨（12/31）  187,000  直接人工  2,800,000 在製品存貨（1/1）  390,000  間接製造成本  5,018,000 在製品存貨（12/31）  276,000  行銷管理費用  950,000 製成品存貨（1/1）  402,000  辦公大樓租金費用  1,200,000 製成品存貨（12/31）  561,000  呆帳費用  176,000 請問豐星鋼鐵廠X5年的銷貨成本為：', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00966', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '京城公司原按賒銷淨額的1%提列壞帳。X3年度賒銷淨額為$2,800,000，該年曾沖銷壞帳$5,000，X3 年底調整後之備抵壞帳餘額為$20,000。若京城公司於X3年中改採帳齡分析法，估計4%的應收帳款 無法收回，已知X3年期初應收帳款餘額$350,000，X3年度應收帳款收現數為$2,600,000，則X3年 度在帳齡分析法下，京城公司應提列的壞帳費用為：', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00967', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '大禮公司於X5年1月1日依面額$5,000,000發行非累積非參加之特別股，用以購買新型工具機，發 行日之市場利率為5%。契約明訂大禮公司必須在X8年1月1日以$5,788,125贖回全部特別股。請 問大禮公司X6年12月31日應認列多少利息費用？', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00968', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '若甲公司有下列事項，其中總共有多少項，應調整X6年的財務報表科目餘額？', '["重要客戶蘋果公司因財務狀況惡化而於X7年初破產，導致甲公司無法如數收回對蘋果公司的全部 應收帳款", "甲公司於甲仙的廠房於X7年初受颱風侵襲而造成重大損失", "甲公司帳載遞延所得稅資產，因X7年初立法院修正所得稅法，而發生重大的不利影響", "甲公司於X7年初為子公司提供財務擔保 項  項  項  項"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00969', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '若甲公司有下列三筆負債，試問在X6年財務報表中，應列示為流動負債之金額為何？', '["銀行借款$100,000，將於X7年3月31日到期。甲公司已於X6年底前，向銀行提出申請展延還款 期限三年，並於X7年1月15日獲得銀行同意", "銀行借款$100,000，將於X7年1月31日到期。甲公司於X6年底前，已經計劃展延還款期限三年， 並於X7年1月15日提出申請，且獲得銀行同意", "於X6年初平價發行面額$100,000、6年期的可轉換公司債，債權人可自X8年12月31日起以面 額將該公司債轉換為甲公司的普通股", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00970', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲公司X6年底帳載存貨金額為$500,000，但仍有下列待釐清存貨事項，試問X6年底甲公司存貨的 正確金額為何？', '["甲公司於X6年12月25日向供應商訂購存貨$100,000，同年12月31日前尚未收到且未入帳。經 查貨物仍在運送途中，起運點交貨", "寄銷於友好公司的存貨價值$100,000，已包含於帳載存貨中", "分期付款出售存貨一批，成本$100,000、售價$200,000，已於X6年12月1日運交給顧客，但因收 款具有高度不確定性，故仍包含於帳載存貨中", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00971', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '若甲公司於調整下列二筆交易前的流動比率為2，調整後的流動比率為3。請問甲公司調整前的流動 資產總金額為何？', '["乙客戶以現金$50,000清償對甲公司的應付帳款", "甲公司支付$50,000現金以清償對丙供應商的應付帳款", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00972', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關投資性不動產的敘述，何者正確？ 企業若因帳務成本不符經濟效益時，可將先前已依公允價值模式衡量之投資性不動產改為使用成 本模式衡量 承租人在營業租賃下持有之不動產權益，若選擇將其認列為投資性不動產，則可自行選擇採用公 允價值模式或是成本模式 企業若將自用不動產轉列為投資性不動產，其當天帳面價值及公允價值之差異應認列為當期損益 將存貨轉換為按公允價值列報之投資性不動產，該不動產於用途改變日之公允價值與原帳面金額 間之差額應認列為損益', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00973', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據商業會計法第68條的規定，商業負責人應於會計年度終了後多久之內，將商業之決算報表提請 商業出資人、合夥人或股東承認？ 三個月  四個月  五個月  六個月', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00974', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '中秋公司於 X6 年初以$100,000 購買專供種植柚子樹的土地，並於 X6 年間為種植柚子而支出 $10,000，X6年底產出公允價值為$20,000的柚子。若中秋公司將柚子運至市場販售需支付必要成本 $10,000，試為中秋公司依據國際會計準則第41號公報（IAS41），計算應列示於X6年資產負債表 上之農產品金額？', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00975', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲公司於X1年初發行5年期公司債，面額$1,000,000，票面利率為10%，市場利率為8%，每年12 月31日付息。試問下列何者敘述正確？ 年間的現金流出為$1,080,000  年初的公司債帳面金額為$1,018,518 年間的利息費用為$80,000  年間的溢價攤銷為$20,000', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00976', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲公司於X1年初以$400,000建造完成A設備，並立即出租予乙公司，租期3年，每年年底可向乙 公司收取租金$200,000。此租賃符合融資租賃，估計租賃結束時的設備殘值為$100,000，但該殘值未 獲得乙公司及第三人的保證。若租賃開始日該設備的公允價值為$500,000，市場利率為5%，試問甲 公司計算因出租設備，而應於X1年間認列銷貨成本的金額為何？', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00977', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲公司X1年部分會計科目如下： 科目    X1年初    X1年底 應付帳款    $40,000    $30,000 存貨    25,000    45,000 預付租金    40,000    50,000 甲公司X1年度損益表上銷貨成本$500,000，租金費用$100,000。試依上述資料，計算甲公司X1年 度直接法下進貨及租金之現金流量為何？ 減少$610,000  減少$620,000  減少$630,000  減少$640,000', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00978', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲公司於X7年間自顧客收到的現金為$450,000，甲公司當年度的銷貨收入為$500,000，期初應收帳 款為$300,000，期末應收帳款為$400,000。若期初預收收入為$100,000，試問甲公司 X7 年底預收收 入的金額為何？', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00979', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '小英計劃自X9年1月1日起，連續5年，每年年底自退休金帳戶中提領$100,000。若年利率為8%， 試為小英計算為達成目標而需於X5年12月31日存入的金額為？ 現值表 1年  2年  3年  4年  5年  6年', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00980', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '926  0.857  0.794  0.735  0.681  0.630', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 0, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00981', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '巨陸公司聘任一菜鳥記帳士協助帳務處理，其編製九月底試算表如下： 借方餘額      貸方餘額 現金與銀行存款   $200,000 預付保險費         $65,000 固定資產   450,000 累計折舊   100,000 預收租金         160,000 權利金收入         515,000 應付公司債         300,000 應付公司債折價         15,000 薪資費用   280,000 現金股利         65,000 合計   $1,030,000     $1,220,000 巨陸公司所有會計科目均有正常餘額，則正確之試算表應有： 借方總額$1,075,000    借方總額$1,125,000 貸方總額$1,120,000    貸方總額$1,140,000', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00982', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '阪神衣飾向市政府承租攤位，租金$100,000，用以販賣世界大學運動會之紀念服裝，每件進貨成本為 $120，刊登網路廣告花費$50,000，預計可銷售1,000件，若阪神衣飾希望賺得稅前淨利$80,000，則 每件紀念服裝應定價：', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "69dbe7191c6b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "960c5b78db01", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 25, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00983', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-a2a4e0d3', 'sub-bookkeeper-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '財政部所發布之新解釋函令，對於尚未核課確定案件之效力適用情形為何？ 立即完全適用    不可適用 不利於納稅義務人之解釋函令可追溯適用  有利於納稅義務人之解釋函令可追溯適用', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "94033dba30f4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "57df1534c299", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "稅務相關法規概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00984', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-a2a4e0d3', 'sub-bookkeeper-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依現行稅捐稽徵法第48條之2的規定，違反稅法規定應處罰鍰之行為，其情節輕微，或漏稅在一定金額 以下者，下列敘述何者正確？ 加計利息    漏稅罰加重 漏稅罰、行為罰部分得減輕或免予處罰  僅行為罰得減輕處罰', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "94033dba30f4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "57df1534c299", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "稅務相關法規概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00985', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-a2a4e0d3', 'sub-bookkeeper-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依現行稅捐稽徵法之規定，關於稅捐核課期間之起算，下列敘述何者正確？ 納稅義務人未於規定期間內申報，但無故意以詐欺或其他不正當方法逃漏稅捐者，核課期間為5年 納稅義務人已在規定期間內申報，但故意以不正當方法逃漏稅者，核課期間為7年 納稅義務人已於規定期間內申報，且無故意以詐欺或其他不正當方法逃漏稅捐者，核課期間自規定申 報期間屆滿之翌日起算 納稅義務人未於規定期間內申報，核課期間自申報日起算7年', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "94033dba30f4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "57df1534c299", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "稅務相關法規概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00986', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-106-a2a4e0d3', 'sub-bookkeeper-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依現行稅捐稽徵法之規定，有關租稅保全之規定，下列敘述何者正確？ 納稅義務人顯有隱匿或移轉財產者，稽徵機關得限制納稅義務人強制出境 納稅義務人欠繳應納稅捐者，稽徵機關通知有關機關，不得為財產移轉或設定他項權利 納稅義務人於稅捐法定徵收日期前，申請離境者，稽徵機關得聲請法院就其財產實施假扣押 納稅義務人就其所欠稅款已依破產法規定和解者，稽徵機關得函請內政部警政署限制其出境', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "94033dba30f4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "57df1534c299", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "602", "s": "1204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "稅務相關法規概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL)
